Plan ahead with the full line-up for this weekend’s Illumination event in Cairns by: GET ROCKING: This weekend’s Illumination event will feature acts including Shades of Gray and Legacy. PICTURE: SILVER GEM CAIRNS Source: Supplied 
CHECK out the line-up for this Saturday’s Illumination Cairns Annual White Party event.
